From b7b7e034998ed22494b315e66acc0fd24cd61541 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harsh Kumar Bijlani <quic_hbijlani@quicinc.com>
Date: Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:34:15 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] wifi: ath12k: Define ath12k_dp_peer structure & APIs for
 create & delete

As part of peer modularization in Unified Driver Framework, station view
for the data path is shown below:

        ath12k_dp_peer
               |
               |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer
               |
               |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer
               |
               |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer

where:
ath12k_dp_peer is newly introduced structure and represents the data path
version of corresponding ath12k_sta.

This ath12k_dp_peer contains the fields used in the per pkt Tx Rx paths
applicable across all the links and maintains an array of
ath12k_dp_link_peer. Per pkt Tx and Rx path operates on ath12k_dp_peer.

ath12k_dp_link_peer contains the fields specific to a link and these are
mostly for telemetry and monitor usage.

Final view of station in UD is shown below:

                Common Path                      Data Path
        -------------------------------------------------------------------
        ath12k_sta                           ath12k_dp_peer
            |                                       |
            |-> ath12k_link_sta    <---->           |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer
            |                                       |
            |-> ath12k_link_sta    <---->           |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer
            |                                       |
            |-> ath12k_link_sta    <---->           |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer

This patch is to define the structure for ath12k_dp_peer and also define
APIs for creation and deletion based on STA state.

Also, structure ath12k_ml_peer is just created and deleted for MLO peers at the
time of connect and disconnect and there is no other use case of this.

Remove this structure and the list "ml_peers" present in ath12k_hw
maintaining linked list of ath12k_ml_peer.

APIs removed:
 ath12k_peer_ml_find()
 ath12k_peer_ml_create()
 ath12k_peer_ml_delete()

Signed-off-by: Harsh Kumar Bijlani <quic_hbijlani@quicinc.com>
